== 8...O-O ==
Black quickly castles their king to safety. This gives Black the option of playing 9...Bg6, which prevents 10. e4 and results in positions where White doesn't get as much central control.

White's main option is still '''[[/9. Qe2/]]''', threatening to play 10. e4.

White can also opt for '''[[/9. Nh4/]]''', transposing into the '''Bled attack'''.

